1. Kupila sam nove *čizme* za zimu. (I bought new *boots* for winter.)
2. Noge su mi bile mokre od snega jer nisam obula *čizme*. (My feet were wet from the snow because I didn't wear *boots*.)
3. Moj brat ima dve para *čizama*. (My brother has two pairs of *boots*.)
4. Zaboravio sam da sam ostavio *čizme* u hodniku. (I forgot that I left my *boots* in the hallway.)
5. Žena je obula *čizme* i izašla iz kuće. (The woman put on her *boots* and left the house.)
6. Nisam mogao pronaći svoje *čizme* jer su bile skrivene ispod kreveta. (I couldn't find my *boots* because they were hidden under the bed.)
7. Devojčica je pokisla na kiši jer nije imala *čizme*. (The girl got soaked in the rain because she didn't have *boots*.)
8. Očistila sam svoje *čizme* od blata nakon šetnje. (I cleaned my *boots* from mud after the walk.)
9. Moj deda nosi stare, ali udobne *čizme*. (My grandfather wears old but comfortable *boots*.)
10. Tražila sam po prodavnicama *čizme* koje su udobne i pristupačne. (I was looking for *boots* that are comfortable and affordable in the shops.)